SUMMARY:MTG Strixhaven: Omens of Chaos: Book Signing
DTSTAMP:20260404T044000Z
DTSTART:20260416T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come meet the author and get your book signed! She will be hang
	ing out and playing Magic with us later as well. The first Magic the gathe
	ring print novel since 2019! This special first edition hardcover includes
	 a Command Tower Magic: The Gathering card with all-new Strixhaven artwork
	. Strixhaven University welcomes you. Begin your magical studies on a fara
	way plane\, encountering new friends\, mysteries\, and dangers\, in this f
	antastical dark academia. Details in the ticket\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcit
